ğŸ”„ 2. Git Rebase
ğŸ” Concept:
Moves your feature branch commits and replays them on top of another branch.
Rewrites history (changes commit hashes).

ğŸ“˜ Example:
You have:

mathematica

main:    A---B---C
feature:         \---D---E
